snippet: Sun Yang of China did not show up for the 1,500-meter-freestyle final at the world championships in Kazan, Russia, creating chaos minutes before the race.
abstract: Chinese swimmer Sun Yang, who served three-month doping suspension in 2014, fails to show up for 1,500-meter-freestyle final at Kazan, Russia, world championships; race is won by Gregorio Paltrinieri of Italy; other swimming news noted.
lead_paragraph: Sun Yang of China did not show up for the 1,500-meter-freestyle final at the world championships in Kazan, Russia, creating chaos minutes before the race.

headline.main: A No-Show in the 1,500 at the Worlds
